'''Bruce Jones''' has been a comic-book writer for over 30 years, best known for his horror comics published by [[Marvel Comics]] in the 1970s. He scripted the four-issue [[Dark Horse Comics]] adaptation of [[Star Wars: A New Hope - The Special Edition|''Star Wars: A New Hope Special Edition'']] in 1997. He is also credited as writer for ''[[Tales from Mos Eisley: Heggs' Tale]]''.

